Vishnick McGovern Milizio LLP is a full-service law firm providing legal counsel and representation in a variety of areas. Our office is located in Lake Success, Nassau County, New York. We are seeking a full-time paralegal/legal assistant for our trusts & estates department.

Requirements:

* Minimum 3 years experience in drafting wills, health care proxies, powers of attorney, trusts and related transfer documents;
* Minimum 3 years experience with administering estates and trusts, trust funding, MHL Art. 81 Guardianships and SCPA Art. 17 Guardianships;
* Experience calendaring court dates/deadlines and e-filings;

The ideal candidate must be a motivated self-starter with the following skills:

* Strong computer/technology skills and the ability to learn new applications:
* Strong written and oral communication skills;
* Be extremely attentive to detail;
* Excellent multi-tasking and organizational skills;
* Be a team player.

Responsibilities:

* Complete administrative duties such as making copies, answering phone calls, mailings, coordinate appointments;
* Draft wills, health care proxies, powers of attorney, trusts and related transfer documents;
* Draft applications for probate and administration forms;
* Manage legal documentation and correspondence in strict confidence;
* Correspond with counsel, court and clients.

Benefits:

* Paid time off;
* Health Insurance contribution;
* 401k participation;
* Long term disability insurance.

This is a full time, in-office position in Lake Success, New York.

Please do not apply if you do not have the required experience.

Job Type: Full-time

Pay: $60,000.00 - $75,000.00 per year

Benefits:

* 401(k)
* Health insurance
* Paid time off

Schedule:

* 8 hour shift
* Monday to Friday

Education:

* High school or equivalent (Required)

Experience:

* Wills, trusts & estate law: 3 years (Required)

Work Location: In person
